text: Seehof () is a municipality in the administrative district of Jura bernois in the canton of Bern in Switzerland. This is one of two German speaking cities in the majority French-speaking Bernese Jura (Jura bernois). The other is Schelten.Historisches Lexikon der Schweiz (HLS), Schwabe AG, Basel, (2002-) == References == Category:Municipalities in Jura bernois
